window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When the witch built the 40-flight tower, she made very sure to do the whole thing properly. Each flight contains a dreadful monster, ranging from a diamond-scaled dragon to a pack of slavering goblins. Should a prince battle his way to the top, he will be rewarded with a golden sword - and the lovely Princess Floralinda.&nbsp;</p> <p>But no prince has managed to conquer the <i>first </i>flight yet, let alone get to the 40th.&nbsp;</p> <p>In fact, the supply of fresh princes seems to have quite dried up.</p>"; 
